s</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Fun relaxing gameplay</strong> easy to pick up and play, yet challenging</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Challenging holes</strong> Navigate through challenging terrains as you find your way to the hole</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Compete for online high scores</strong> show of your skills and become the golf pro</li></ul><br>",
